The purpose of this study is to investigate the contents in blood sampled from surgery site during hip replacement compared with blood sampled from abdominal aortic surgery.

 Is there any difference in pro-inflammatory cytokines (IL-1beta, IL-6, IL-8 and TNF-), complement activation (C3a)?